input.value:
fetch dt.system.query_executions
| filterout matchesPhrase(user, "dynatrace")
| filterout user == "graildemo2023@gmail.com"
| summarize count=count(), by:{user}
| sort count desc

grail.canonicalQuery:

| filter isFalseOrNull(matchesPhrase(user, "dynatrace"))

| sort count, direction:"descending"
